,[180,188,194,200],{"type":181,"tag":182,"props":183,"children":185},"element","h2",{"id":184},"概述",[186],{"type":187,"value":184},"text",{"type":181,"tag":189,"props":190,"children":191},"p",{},[192],{"type":187,"value":193},"Sidecar 模式是一种设计模式，通常用于微服务架构中。它涉及将一个辅助容器（sidecar）与主应用程序容器一起部署在同一个 Pod 中。Sidecar 容器负责处理与主应用程序相关的辅助任务，如日志收集、配置管理、服务发现等，从而使主应用程序能够专注于其核心功能。",{"type":181,"tag":182,"props":195,"children":197},{"id":196},"domain",[198],{"type":187,"value":199},"Domain",{"type":181,"tag":201,"props":202,"children":203},"ul",{},[204],{"type":181,"tag":205,"props":206,"children":207},"li",{},[208],{"type":181,"tag":209,"props":210,"children":212},"a",{"href":211},"/maps/_cloud-native/sidecar/service-mesh-without-sidecar",[213],{"type":187,"value":214},"Service Mesh without Sidecar",{"title":175,"searchDepth":216,"depth":216,"links":217},2,[218,219],{"id":184,"depth":216,"text":184},{"id":196,"depth":216,"text":199},"markdown","content:6.maps:_cloud-native:sidecar:sidecar.md","content","6.maps/_cloud-native/sidecar/sidecar.md","6.maps/_cloud-native/sidecar/sidecar","md",[227,230],{"_path":211,"title":228,"description":229},"无边车的服务网格","随着基于 sidecar 的服务网格在成本和运维复杂度上的问题持续存在，我们很高兴看到出现了另一种不依赖 sidecar 的服务网格选项：Istio Ambient 模式。",{"_path":231,"title":232,"description":233},"/maps/_communication","Communication","Communication is the process of exchanging information, ideas, thoughts, and feelings.",1771214212043]